

**Matsh g Jesus ha gegos g giꞌik mihl chechoj ch muꞌi ehp **

*An g neid g Matthew 15:32-39 *

1 Kush pi shaꞌi tash amjed. Tsh muꞌi am ep i e hemapai g hemajkam k ab kaiham g Jesus waik tashkaj. Sh hahawa pi an hu haꞌichug mas haschu wo huh. Tsh g Jesus am i ha wai g e‑chuhchai k hah ha ahg, 2 “Neh, waik tashkaj o in waꞌi t‑wehmaj idam hemajkam ch heki hu waꞌi pi haꞌichu huh. Ni s‑ha hoꞌigeꞌid. 3 Tp hems haꞌijj wo s‑e chuhugi matp gam hu wo sha hihi pi haꞌichu hugok.” 

4 Sh hegam ab i kakke, “Kuchs hebai hig wo ui g haꞌichu hugi mat wehs wo ha aꞌahe idam?” 

5 Sh ab ep ha kakke, “Heꞌekia at am i wih g sismito?” 

Sh hab kaij, “Wewaꞌak” 

6 Jesus atsh am hahawa ha ahgi g hemajkam mat am wo dadhaiwua. Kush am dadhaiwua. Tsh am ui g sismito k ab hoꞌigeꞌel g Jiosh k am hahawa hahain k ha mah g e‑chuhchai. Kutsh an i ha mahkhi g hemajkam. 

7 Kumsh am hi wa haꞌi al toꞌakch g waptopi. Kutsh ab ep hoꞌigeꞌel g Jiosh k am ha ahgi mat an ep wo i ha mahkhi. Tsh hab e juh. 8 Tsh wehsijj hug k oi wa hi si s‑kokwod, chum as am hu hebai d i giꞌik mihl chechoj ch muꞌijj g uꞌuwi ch aꞌal. 9 Tsh g Jesus chuhchai an i uꞌihi g wihpiꞌidaj mat am huꞌi wewaꞌak hoha wo ha shuhshud. 

Kutsh g Jesus am hahawa ha ahgi g hemajkam mat gam hu wo hihi. 10 Tsh idam Jesus am ha hekaj i chehchsh wahlko ch ed k gam hu hihi mash am Dalmanutha chekshani k am i huhud. 

**Mamsh ab chum chehani g Jesus mat am wo ha chehgi g s‑hasig haꞌichu **

*An g neid g Matthew 16:1-4 *

11 Kutsh am haꞌi dada g Palasi k ab neꞌowin g Jesus ch ab chum si chehani mat g si s‑hasig haꞌichu am wo ha chehgi matp woho d Jiosh si Kehsha. 

12 Kutsh g Jesus am si ihbuiwua k hab kaij, “Kus haschu ahgch ab ni‑kakke idam hemajkam mant g si s‑hasig haꞌichu am wo ha chehgi. Si ant s‑wohom hab wo chei mant pi am hu wo shaꞌi ha chehgi g si s‑hasig haꞌichu.” 13 Neh bash kaij ch am hahawa ha dagito. Kutsh an ep i chehchsh wahlko ch ed k gam hu aigo ep hihi. 

**Mattsh pi ha oidk wo haꞌichu chegito g pi wohochuddam **

*An g neid g Matthew 16:5-12 *

14 Tsh eda pi chegito idam mat wo ui g sismito. Kush hemako am kahch. 15 Sh hab kaij g Jesus am ha wui, “Si g wo s‑e nenꞌoidk mat pi wo em‑cheawuagi g ha‑jewajidakud hegam Palasi ch hegam mo ab si has elid g Herod.” 

16 Sh hegam chuhchaij am hahawa aꞌaga ch hab kaij ab aꞌai e wui, “Heg oki hekaj hab kaij mach pi ha sismitoga” 

17 Kush eda g Jesus s‑ha amichud mo has kaij ch hab ha ahg, “Pi amki koi amichud mani heꞌes edgid g gewkdag ch hekaj am aꞌaga mach pi ha sismitoga. 18 Am am wa chum neid mant al hetasp sismitokaj ha gegos g hetasp mihl chechoj ch muꞌi ehp. Pegih, namt pi chegito 19 mamt heꞌekia i hoha shuhshud k ui g wihpiꞌidaj?” 

Kush hab kaij, “Gamai gohk.” 

20 Sh hab ep kaij g Jesus, “Kumt heꞌekia i hoha shuhshud k ui g wihpiꞌidaj mant al wewaꞌak sismitokaj am ha gegos hegam giꞌik mihl chechoj ch muꞌi ehp?” 

Sh hab kaij, “Wewaꞌak.” 

21 Kush hab kaij g Jesus, “Pegih, mt wo chum s‑mahchk mani heꞌes i edgid g gewkdag ch hab wo s‑amich mani pi heg hab ahg sismito ch wabshaba haꞌichu chum em‑tashogid ch heg am wepogid g jewajidakud.” 

**Matsh g Jesus am hema doaj g pi neadam Bethsaida t am **

22 Kutsh gam hu dada Bethsaida t am k am i huhud. Kutsh g hemajkam am hema uꞌapa g oꞌodham Jesus wui mash pi nea k ab i e shoꞌigch wui mat ab wo taht. 23 Kutsh an bei g pi neadam nowij an k am i wanimed k gam hu i wuhshad ab kihhim t amjed k ab hahawa siswua wuhpuij ab k ab ep taht k ab kakke, “Shahchu ap hig neid?” 

24 Tsh ab i nen k hab kaij, “Neid ani mo an oiopo g hemajkam ch wabshaba hab sha mahs mo g uꞌus wuhshanim.” 

25 Tsh ab ep taht g wuhpuij. Kutsh ab ep i nea. Tsh g wuhpuij am i apꞌet. Sh hahawa wehs haꞌichu si s‑ap neid. 26 Sh g Jesus hab ahg matsh gam hu uhpam wo hih e‑kihdag wui k pi am hu wo kia i wah kihhim ch ed. 

**Matsh g Peter am ah mo hedai wud g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 16:13-20; Luke 9:18-21 *

27 Kutsh gam hu hahawa hihi idam Jesus am haꞌi ep ha wui g kihhim am miabidch g Cesaria Philippi kihhim. Kush g Jesus ab ha kakke ch hab kaij, “Am g wo ni‑ahgid, dohꞌo ni‑elid g hemajkam?” 

28 Kush hab kaij, “Haꞌijj o hab m‑elid map d hegai Johnbad mo chum t‑pahl wapkonahim ch haꞌijj hab ep m‑elid map d Elijabad o hema i ehp hegam kekelibad Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam.” 

29 Sh ab ep ha kakke g Jesus, “Kum ahpim hig hedai ni‑elid?” 

Kush g Peter hab kaij, “Dap Jiosh si Kehsha maptsh ab wo i wuhsh si haꞌichu wehhejed.” 

30 Kush hab ha ahg mat pi hedai wo shaꞌi ha ahgi hemu mo hedai wud. 

**Mash g Jesus am ha ahgid matsh wo e shoꞌigchud k wo e muhkid **

*An g neid g Matthew 16:21-28; Luke 9:22-27 *

31 Neh, tsh am i amjed am hahawa haꞌichu ha mashcha ab e amjed hab kaijch mat hemho wa muꞌi wo e shoꞌigch g Jiosh si Kehsha. Kutsh pi ab hu wo tatchua g geꞌeged ch uꞌugchu papal ch chehanig t‑mashchamdam k am wo i dagito mat wo e‑muhkid. Tsh amjed d wo i waik tashk, tsh ep wo e‑chegito. 32 Neh, sh id am si tasho ha ahgid. 

Kutsh g Peter im hu goꞌolko i be k ab si s‑gewkam neok wui hab kaijch mat pi woho hab wo e juh. 

33 Kutsh wabshaba g Jesus ab haꞌab i kekiwua ha wui k ab epai si s‑gewkam neo ab wui g Peter hab kaijch, “Pi g shaꞌi ni‑shohbid. Do wabsh hejel hab m‑elida ihda. Kup ab wui kehk g Jiosh hab elida hab masma mo g ge Jiawul.” 

34 Sh eda muꞌij g hemajkam an ha wehgaj. Kutsh ab i ha waid k hab ha ahg, “Mamtp am wo s‑oidam g ni‑himdag k hemho wa gam hu wo dagito g hejel e‑tatchui k ahni ni‑tatchui hab wo junihid ni‑wehhejed e shoꞌigchudch. Heg at wo wa wepok mam ab mohto g kots ch ab ab wo e muhkid. 35 Pi amt wo heki wua g e‑doakag mamtp wo hekaj am ni‑wehhejed. Heg at wo heki wua g e‑doakag matp hedai wo chum s‑daꞌad. 

36 “Pi at haꞌichu wehhejed wo s‑kehgajk matp g oꞌodham wehs wo bei mo haschu i tatchua id dahm jewed k wabshaba pi wo e doꞌibia. 37 Pi o an hu haꞌichug id dahm jewed mas heg hekaj wo e doꞌibia g oꞌodham. 

38 “Muꞌi hemajkam at wabsh s‑tahhadam hab wo junihid g pi apꞌekam ch wo pi em‑haꞌichuchudad. Kumt wabshaba ahpim pi wo si e elidad ni‑hekaj ch hekaj g ni‑mashchamadag. Nt ahni hab waꞌap pi wo si ni‑elidad em‑hekaj mant hekid ia ep wo jiwia. Idani at ab ni‑ab si s‑tondam wo e chehgidad g ni‑ohg gewkdag. T g muꞌi anghil ni‑wehm ab wo i hihi.” 

